"Blender is a free and open-source 3D computer \ngraphics software toolset used for creating \nanimated films, visual effects, art, 3D printed \nmodels, motion graphics, interactive 3D \napplications, virtual reality and computer games. \nBlender's features include 3D modeling, UV \nunwrapping, texturing, raster graphics editing, \nrigging and skinning, fluid and smoke simulation, \nparticle simulation, soft body simulation, \nsculpting, animating, match moving, rendering, \nmotion graphics, video editing, and compositing."